OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776819790
OL,3,CDeaf and blind poodle-cross Colin
OL,4,Cneeds a new home after mass pet rescue
OL,6,FA deaf and blind dog called Colin is
OL,7,Fin need of a new home following a mass
OL,8,Fpet rescue.
OL,10,FThe three-year-old, miniature poodle-
OL,11,Fcross was one of 250 dogs recently
OL,12,Frescued from a single household.
OL,14,FHe was taken on by the Dogs Trust
OL,15,FShoreham and they're searching for a
OL,16,Fspecial home where he can thrive.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
