CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776819790
OL,3,CDeaf and blind poodle-cross Colin
OL,4,Cneeds a new home after mass pet rescue
OL,6,FDog welfare supervisor, Amy Clements,
OL,7,Fsaid he copes well with his
OL,8,Fdisabilities, "Anytime we go anywhere
OL,9,Fnew we take him on a lead and let him
OL,10,Fexplore the area.
OL,12,F"He walks with his legs up so that can
OL,13,Fmap out wherever he is first then he
OL,14,Fjust remembers where everything is. He
OL,15,Fcan go anywhere, he loves to go to the
OL,16,Fbeach, he's doing so so well
OL,17,Fconsidering.
OL,19,F"He is the sweetest boy, he loves to
OL,20,Fplay with toys and just loves to have
OL,21,Fa little cuddle."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
