PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776819790
OL,3,CDeaf and blind poodle-cross Colin
OL,4,Cneeds a new home after mass pet rescue
OL,6,FRehoming manager, Kirsty Hayward, says
OL,7,Fthey're looking for a home that is
OL,8,Fpatient and understanding of his
OL,9,Fcircumstances.
OL,11,F"We be really excited to hear from
OL,12,Fpeople that have any experience with
OL,13,Frehabilitating dogs that have any sort
OL,14,Fof disability, but that's by no means
OL,15,Fabsolutely necessary.
OL,17,F"All of the doodles that we rehome
OL,18,Fwill be in pairs, so obviously with
OL,19,FColin, a home with a stable happy dog
OL,20,Fthat already lives there for company."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
