PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776819790
OL,3,CDeaf and blind poodle-cross Colin
OL,4,Cneeds a new home after mass pet rescue
OL,6,FMore than 250 poodle-cross dogs were
OL,7,Ffound at the same property earlier
OL,8,Fthis year.
OL,10,FThe RSPCA took in 87 dogs while 159
OL,11,Fwent to the Dogs Trust.
OL,13,FAccording to the RSPCA, the living
OL,14,Fconditions and number of dogs had
OL,15,Fspiralled out of control "due to
OL,16,Fextenuating family circumstances".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
