PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776819790
OL,3,CDeaf and blind poodle-cross Colin
OL,4,Cneeds a new home after mass pet rescue
OL,6,FAn image of the dogs was deemed so
OL,7,Fshocking that the animal welfare
OL,8,Fcharity was forced to refute
OL,9,Fallegations it was developed by
OL,10,Fartificial intelligence.
OL,12,FLast year, more than 4000 rescues
OL,13,Facross the country involved at least
OL,14,F10 animals, with just under 400
OL,15,Fincidents in the south.
OL,17,FOther recent large-scale rescues
OL,18,Finclude an incident where 20 guinea
OL,19,Fpigs were signed over from a property
OL,20,Fin the South by an owner who was
OL,21,Fstruggling to cope.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
