PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776819790
OL,3,CDeaf and blind poodle-cross Colin
OL,4,Cneeds a new home after mass pet rescue
OL,6,FIn Dorset, the number of incidents
OL,7,Finvolving more than ten animals rose
OL,8,Ffrom 33 in 2024 to 53 last year.
OL,10,FThere was a similar rise in Wiltshire,
OL,11,Fwhich increased from 24 incidents to
OL,12,F40 across the same period.
OL,14,FAnimal charities are urging people
OL,15,Fconsidering adding a pet to their
OL,16,Ffamily, to consider adopting, to help
OL,17,Ffree-up space in their overwhelmed
OL,18,Fcentres, and to help ease the pressure
OL,19,Fcaused by so many multi-animal cases.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
